Package: lefser
Type: Package
Title: R implementation of the LEfSE method for microbiome biomarker discovery
Description: lefser uses Kruskal-Wallis test, Wilcoxon-Rank Sum test, and LDA
  to find biomarkers of groups and sub-groups.
Version: 0.99.0
